  <h1 class="gd-h1">Siglufjörður: The Heliski Base Town</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Every Viking Heliskiing trip begins and ends in Siglufjörður, a small, characterful town at the northern edge of Iceland that once ran on herring and now welcomes skiers to the Troll Peninsula. This is a guide to the town itself, its history and its everyday pleasures, before you explore <a href="/packages">the packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
